data.description:
Boater's Paradise,** Assumable uber low mortgage available**.Amazing 2 story Deepwater pool home on approximately 85' of waterfront and a 40' dock with a 10,000lb Boat Lift. Breathtaking water views at the juncture of two 100' wide canals, only two blocks from the St. Lucie River. No direct rear neighbors. Best views in the neighborhood. This magnificent 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 CG pool home has 2 Master Suites, the first one situated on the main level and the second on the second level with spectacular water views. Newer A/C units, and Hurricane Impact Glass throughout. Minutes to the River and 15 minutes to the ocean. No fixed bridges. Albatross Way dead ends at a Cul-De-Sac. **** Please review the items of entire improvements 1629 SW ALBATROSS WAY

LIST OF IMPROVEMENTS

Interior

1) 100% Hurricane Impact Glass throughout 2 Low-E Sliders 2nd level
2) Two Trane energy efficient 16 Seer 3.0 ton and 2.5 ton units replaced inside and out (2019) Serviced annually
3) New A/C Smith ProLine 40 Gallon Water Heater w/ a Thermal Expansion Tank (October 2022)
4) Hurricane Impact Glass throughout
5) New LVP flooring stairs and second level (2022)
6) Shaker Baseboards and Door trim second level (2022)
7) White over Grey kitchen Cabinets
8) Quartz Counter tops
9) Stainless Steel Appliances w/ Induction oven
10) Front Load Washer and Dryer
11) Stainless Steel modern farmhouse sink
12) HansGrohe Commercial Faucet
13) High end custom cabinetry and fixtures in all bathrooms
14) Recessed LED lighting in Entry way, Living Room and Dining Room
15) Newer Ceiling Fans in every room and patio
16) Structural Header in Living/Dining Room for an Open Concept floor plan
17) 1st level throughout, Travertine marble w/ chiseled edge with French pattern
18) Fireplace



Exterior

1) 85' corrugated fiberglass seawall and pool retaining wall with concrete cap (2018)
2) 40' Lumberrock composite dock (2018)
3) Tide Tamer Boat lift approximately 10,000-13,000lbs (2018)
4) All new pool equipment (2022)
5) New Cabana vinyl fence (2022)
6) New side yard fences and gates (2022)
7) New Landscape lighting (2022)
8) New flat roofs on 2nd level (2022)
9) New decking and railing (2022)
10) New gutters
11) New Sherwin Williams Super-Paint and Primer salt water safe
